reqqu = mul.Queue()
resqu = mul.Queue()
content = pd.DataFrame([wthr.HourlyWeatherReport(lat=self.lat, lon=self.lon,
    date=self.day, time=self.time).dict])
req = dict(type='put', args=[content])
reqqu.put(req)
req = dict(pid=os.getpid(), type='get', args=(self.day, self.lat, self.lon))
reqqu.put(req)
reqqu.put(dict(type='end'))
wthr.cache_manager(reqqu, resqu, self.wcname)
res = resqu.get()
self.assertTrue(res['pid'] == os.getpid())
